[p 
	"As my first submission for this game, and also for this site, I think I did pretty well. It shaves off 28 minutes from its own category, and beats the any% glitchless by 1 minute. The glitch in question is called the Infinite Gil Glitch, which exists only in the japanese version, and needs a gameboy advance. For now, it's not possible to TAS it, that's why I'm sticking with glitchless.
	$LF
]p
