[h3 id=Othercomments
 
	" Other comments
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"This movie features optimised fights and routings in the dungeons. Furthermore, I manipulated the RNG a lot, so there is a lot of one frame tricks to better run, including some perfect bonus points.
	$LF
	"Unfortunately, this run is not perfect. My routing mistakes total aproximately 1 minute, this including: talking to my dad too much, missclaculations in Lynari Desert, a detour in Conall Curach and the optimisations of the last bosses. Also, I do not master TAS imputs, so I'm limited to 8 directions.
	$LF
	"I hope you enjoy.
	$LF
